hu.akarnokd.reactive4java.util

Class TaggedCompositeCloseable

  • java.lang.Object
    • hu.akarnokd.reactive4java.util.TaggedCompositeCloseable
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cancelable, Closeable, AutoCloseable

    public class TaggedCompositeCloseable
extends Object
implements Closeable, Cancelable
    A composite, modifyable holder of Closeable values with tag objects. The container ensures that once it is closed, attempts to add new closeables will instantly close them.
    Since:
    0.97
    Author:
    akarnokd, 2013.01.14.
